name: AKIRA Motorbike BATE
description:
This is a lora homage to the AKIRA movie, you can get a complete motorcycle.

Trigger

a red akirabike

Weights

Known Defects!!!

  • AKIRA LoRA will destroy the character's face, so it needs to be used with a helmet tag or cyberhelmet.

  • There will be errors in the structure and details in the close-up.

Matchs

https://civitai.com/models/25360/cyberhelmet-or-wearable-lora

歡迎朋友們加我微信交流：artist3yehe

Reach me on Twitter if you wish to contribute to improving this mod, Thx!

https://twitter.com/Artist3YeHe
